name: FCreateActorParams
doc:
FCreateActorParams is a collection of input data intended to be passed to
UModelingObjectsCreationAPI::CreateNewActor().

TargetWorld: The World/Level the new Actor should be created in (if known).
BaseName: The base name of the new Actor
Transform: The 3D local-to-world transform for the new actor
TemplateAsset: A template Asset used to determine the type of Actor to spawn.
